What's wrong with 'on a position'?

About the message:

1. If I were a developer of an APK I would like to know what is happening and why my APK is not working. Otherwise it will just not work and I will have no way of figuring out what's the problem.

2. This string says nothing about the security. Is is dangerous to print a message?

